<plot>Roar of the Wild is an interactive wild adventure evoked by the call of nature and the urge to explore survival instincts. The show is hosted by Lin Sutherland, a wildlife photographer who has a unique and inapt ability to unearth interesting and stimulating stories many people may have never seen. In this series the audience will gain an insight into a variety of bizarre and colorful wildlife and the often-unusual social and interactive behavior.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?465187</url></doc>
